How to Run the Project
Option 1: Using Live Server in VS Code
Open the project folder in VS Code
Make sure all project files are inside the same root folder
Install the Live Server extension if not already installed
Right-click index.html
Click Open with Live Server
The project will open in your browser
Example local URL:
http://127.0.0.1:5500/index.html
From there, all linked pages such as about.html, mandate.html, and tenders.html should open correctly if they are in the same folder.
 